<p>SCP-8900-EX忽怠协议执行方案</p>
<hr />
<table class="wiki-content-table">
<tr>
<th>指针</th>
<th>结果</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>常态</td>
<td>成为内部</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>颜色</td>
<td>进入内部</td>
</tr>
</table>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;评论区&nbsp;1个</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
