</div>
</div>
<p>20██/██/██ ██:██, 地点：Alto Clef的秘密邮箱-收件箱</p>
<hr />
<p>scp-166了解到了<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/group-date">最近发生在站点里的事件</a>。经调查是由于她听到了两名研究员在测试时的闲谈。目前已经按照规定处理了涉事人员。<br />
她对世间居然有如此淫荡的事情感到非常震怒，认为这是“索多玛一样的渎神“，并且申请得到一张事件现场照片以便能更具体的批评这种行为。</p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;评论区&nbsp;0个</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;评论区</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00107" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/short-stories:00107" target="_blank">编辑 &amp; 评论</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00107-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pinksongluna" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6773826); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6773826&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247435" alt="pinksongluna" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6773826)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pinksongluna" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6773826); return false;">pinksongluna</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1609415515 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">31 Dec 2020 11:51</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<div class="content-panel standalone series">
<div style="text-align: right;">
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;评分</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;评分</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/short-stories:00020/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>20██/██/██ ██:██, 地点：██████</p>
<hr />
<p>你一直想知道把SCP-005插进SCP-004里面会发生什么。</p>
<p>现在你终于知道了。</p>
<p>你看见了门后那令你震惊之物，你所难以解密之可怖之物。</p>
<p>你开始对你过去所熟知的事物产生怀疑。你终于知道了它的真相，但你希望你不知道。</p>
<p>你觉得恶心。</p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;评论区&nbsp;0个</a></div>
