<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00079" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/short-stories:00079" target="_blank">编辑 &amp; 评论</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00079-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/etinjat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4055881); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4055881&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247435" alt="Etinjat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4055881)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/etinjat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4055881); return false;">Etinjat</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1599476991 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">07 Sep 2020 11:09</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<div class="content-panel standalone series">
<div style="text-align: right;">
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;评分</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;评分</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/short-stories:00041/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>20██/██/██ ██:██, 地点：酩酊街</p>
<hr />
<p>遥望无回路<br />
此地徒有雪与夜<br />
居此共酩酊</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;释义</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;没能赶上的B站的俳句竞赛的作品</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>描述的是一个决定在酩酊街居住下来的的人的心理变化过程。<br />
远望已经看不到来时的路了，那我已经无路可回了吧。这里只有无尽的雪与看不到边际的黑夜，空气中弥漫着浓郁的酒香气息，似乎是有什么人在喝酒。远处能看到微光，好像是一个城镇。我一直形影相吊，没有什么可怀念的事物。想到此，我看向城镇的方向，缓缓前行。那就在这里居住下来吧，喝个痛痛快快，酩酊大醉地把想要忘却的事情遗忘掉吧。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;评论区&nbsp;0个</a></div>
