<p><span id="u-credit-00041" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/short-stories:00041" target="_blank">编辑 &amp; 评论</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00041-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/achsab" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4325914); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4325914&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247435" alt="achsab" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4325914)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/achsab" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4325914); return false;">achsab</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1593838875 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">04 Jul 2020 05:01</span></p>
</div>
