<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c8h17oh" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5420288); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5420288&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247435" alt="C8H17OH" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5420288)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c8h17oh" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5420288); return false;">C8H17OH</a></span>：</strong><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">有一点小问题：在世界观内应该称呼为“总部”而非“主站”（又不是只有一个站）。不过还是</span>蛮有趣的，up了。</p>
