<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-destroyerplantard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6516148); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6516148&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247435" alt="Dr DestroyerPlantard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6516148)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-destroyerplantard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6516148); return false;">Dr DestroyerPlantard</a></span>：</strong>我把“Site cn-05”改成了“Site-CN-05”。挺好的，UP了。</p>
