<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00008" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/short-stories:00008" target="_blank">编辑 &amp; 评论</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00008-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raintree" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5375092); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5375092&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247435" alt="RainTree" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5375092)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raintree" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5375092); return false;">RainTree</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1590942162 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">31 May 2020 16:22</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<div class="content-panel standalone series">
<div style="text-align: right;">
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;评分</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;评分</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/short-stories:00059/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>手持两把锟斤拷，口中疾呼烫烫烫</p>
<hr />
<p>在生与死的边界，他向她狠狠的抛出了什么。</p>
<p>“我于深渊中刺向你”</p>
<p>不是Gungnir，也不是Lance of Longinus。</p>
<p>是一根未拆封的波板糖。</p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;评论区&nbsp;0个</a></div>
