<div id="u-credit-00105-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mass-meme" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4588322); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4588322&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247435" alt="Mass-MEME" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4588322)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mass-meme" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4588322); return false;">Mass-MEME</a></span></p>
