<p><span id="u-credit-00005" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/short-stories:00005" target="_blank">编辑 &amp; 评论</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00005-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/higashikatajosuke" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6150792); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6150792&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610247436" alt="HigashikataJosuke" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6150792)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/higashikatajosuke" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6150792); return false;">HigashikataJosuke</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1590937383 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">31 May 2020 15:03</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<div class="content-panel standalone series">
<div style="text-align: right;">
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;评分</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;评分</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/short-stories:00018/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>2021/██/██ ██:██, 地点：site-██上空</p>
<hr />
<p>他看着下方那个正在毁灭site-██的无以名状的存在，一时忘记了自己是来干什么的。</p>
<p>那个存在是终结异常之异常，不到72小时它已无效化了两千多个异常并摧毁了几十个GOI，基金会正在做最后的挣扎。</p>
<p>他想起来了，自己是来轰炸这家伙的。</p>
<p>说实话，连他也不信自己能击败它。他摘下防化面具，用力将胸前的红宝石吊坠扯下。在异常强烈的影响下，脆弱的宝石被他的手指压碎，碎片飞出机舱，被旋翼搅出的狂风吹得四散纷飞，迅捷地消失在弥漫着五彩霞光的天幕中。</p>
<p>“死倒是也不容易。”他喃喃道，按下了发射钮。</p>
<hr />
